signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Quarterbacks with generational arms have the power to stretch any defense to its breaking point. When they enter the zone, their maximum throw distance is increased by 15+ yards.
Passers with this ability have faster passing animations when they are throwing under pressure
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws under 40 yards while running outside the pocket (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability receive better blocking support on designed quarterback run plays.
Passers with this ability have a reduced chance to be impacted by throw penalties caused by defensive pressure while their feet are set in the pocket
QB has increased pass animation speed and a larger threshold before using the long hail mary windup animation
Defenders with this ability will ignore one bar of blocker resistance when attempting swim/club pass rush moves
Defenders with this ability use faster, more dominant pass rush moves while rushing from the edge of the defense.
Defenders with this ability use faster run shed moves for a better chance at shedding blocks against outside zone plays.
Ballcarriers with this ability have steerable juke animations.
Running backs with this ability have better catch in traffic and route running when coming out of the backfield against linebackers and linemen.
Ballcarriers with this ability will frequently attempt to gain extra yards while being tackled
The game's top defenders excel in all situations. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their chance of defeating run blocks, and disrupting catches via tackles.
Defenders with this ability will frequently attempt and win impact blocks against receivers, tight ends, and running backs.
Defenders with this ability will clear a ballcarrier's progress towards entering the zone with a hit-stick tackle.
Defenders with this ability are granted a free pass rush move once per play after spending stamina to perform one
Defenders with this ability do not need to spend stamina on shed attempts during a run play
Defenders with this ability can reach out of engaged blocks to tackle or sack nearby ballcarriers.
Players with this ability will distract defenders for longer with their runoffs
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes 10-20 yards from the LoS, inside the numbers
Receivers with this ability catch more consistently while catching passes less than 10 yards from the LoS.
